<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 12:32:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>科学家创造出可以彻底改变未来计算机的微型“纳米激光”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-create-tiny-nanolaser-that-could-revolutionize-future-computers</link><description>研究人员创造了一种超紧凑的纳米激光器，可以改变数据在微芯片内移动的方式，用光代替电信号。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-create-tiny-nanolaser-that-could-revolutionize-future-computers.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 12:32:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-create-tiny-nanolaser-that-could-revolutionize-future-computers</guid></item><item><title>谜团加深：天体物理学家称暗物质可能不是一回事</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mystery-deepens-astrophysicists-say-dark-matter-may-not-be-one-thing</link><description>一个新模型表明暗物质可能比单一物质更复杂，可能会重塑科学家解释宇宙隐藏结构的方式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mystery-deepens-astrophysicists-say-dark-matter-may-not-be-one-thing.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 12:17:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mystery-deepens-astrophysicists-say-dark-matter-may-not-be-one-thing</guid></item><item><title>没有太阳的生活？科学家称它可能在流浪行星的卫星上繁衍生息</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/life-without-a-sun-scientists-say-it-may-thrive-on-rogue-planet-moons</link><description>科学家提出，围绕在星际空间漂流的自由漂浮行星的卫星上可能存在维持生命的环境。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/life-without-a-sun-scientists-say-it-may-thrive-on-rogue-planet-moons.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 12:02:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/life-without-a-sun-scientists-say-it-may-thrive-on-rogue-planet-moons</guid></item><item><title>科学家发现地幔深处的意外行为</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-uncover-unexpected-behavior-deep-inside-earths-mantle</link><description>常见矿物中的微小缺陷可能会揭示地球内部运动的意想不到的模式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-uncover-unexpected-behavior-deep-inside-earths-mantle.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 11:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-uncover-unexpected-behavior-deep-inside-earths-mantle</guid></item><item><title>35 亿年前的岩石改写了板块构造的故事</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/3-5-billion-year-old-rocks-rewrite-the-story-of-plate-tectonics</link><description>古老的岩石揭示了早期地球在地质上可能根本就不是静止的。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/3-5-billion-year-old-rocks-rewrite-the-story-of-plate-tectonics2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 11:32:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/3-5-billion-year-old-rocks-rewrite-the-story-of-plate-tectonics</guid></item><item><title>后门 Telnyx PyPI 软件包可推送隐藏在 WAV 音频中的恶意软件</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/backdoored-telnyx-pypi-package-pushes-malware-hidden-in-wav-audio</link><description>TeamPCP 黑客今天破坏了 Python 软件包索引上的 Telnyx 软件包，上传了恶意版本，这些版本传播隐藏在 WAV 文件中的凭据窃取恶意软件。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/backdoored-telnyx-pypi-package-pushes-malware-hidden-in-wav-audio.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 11:17:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/backdoored-telnyx-pypi-package-pushes-malware-hidden-in-wav-audio</guid></item><item><title>GitHub 上的虚假 VS Code 警报向开发人员传播恶意软件</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/fake-vs-code-alerts-on-github-spread-malware-to-developers</link><description>一项大规模活动针对 GitHub 上的开发人员，在各个项目的讨论部分发布虚假的 Visual Studio Code (VS Code) 安全警报，诱骗用户下载恶意软件。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/fake-vs-code-alerts-on-github-spread-malware-to-developers.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 11:02:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/fake-vs-code-alerts-on-github-spread-malware-to-developers</guid></item><item><title>Agentic GRC：团队获取技术。思维方式的转变是缺失的</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/agentic-grc-teams-get-the-tech-the-mindset-shift-is-whats-missing</link><description>Agentic GRC 使工作流程自动化，迫使团队重新思考他们在运营之外的角色。轶事解释了为什么最大的挑战是从执行转向风险领导。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/agentic-grc-teams-get-the-tech-the-mindset-shift-is-whats-missing2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 10:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/agentic-grc-teams-get-the-tech-the-mindset-shift-is-whats-missing</guid></item><item><title>AitM 网络钓鱼利用 Cloudflare Turnstile 规避攻击 TikTok 企业帐户</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/aitm-phishing-targets-tiktok-business-accounts-using-cloudflare-turnstile-evasion</link><description>由于与 BianLian 相关的 SVG 恶意软件针对委内瑞拉，AitM 网络钓鱼通过 Cloudflare Turnstile 规避劫持了 TikTok Business 帐户。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/aitm-phishing-targets-tiktok-business-accounts-using-cloudflare-turnstile-evasion2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 10:32:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/aitm-phishing-targets-tiktok-business-accounts-using-cloudflare-turnstile-evasion</guid></item><item><title>能源危机导致肿瘤中的 T 细胞耗尽</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/energy-crisis-drives-t-cells-to-exhaustion-in-tumors</link><description>免疫系统的杀伤性 T 细胞在检测和消灭癌细胞方面发挥着值得称赞的作用。但肿瘤中心的恶劣环境常常会削弱它们的活力，使它们陷入一种永久的倦怠状态，称为“终极疲惫”。这种现象解释了为什么如此多的肿瘤抵抗常规免疫清除，甚至抵抗旨在刺激其致死能力的癌症免疫疗法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/energy-crisis-drives-t-cells-to-exhaustion-in-tumors2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 10:17:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/energy-crisis-drives-t-cells-to-exhaustion-in-tumors</guid></item></channel></rss>